{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "排演一齣悲劇", "storyInfo": "布景噴畫師蒂比舉辦的觀影會中途，謝莉收到一則訊息後匆忙離開，最終死於倉庫的冷凍庫內。與此同時，潛入劇組辦公室的盧西恩發現了被刻意隱藏的另一個秘密。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_oldtv", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深夜，本應空無一人的道具間傳來細碎的聲響和被壓抑的悲鳴。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幽暗的角落裡，道具假人沒有五官的面孔被閃爍的螢光打亮。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比抱著靠枕縮在沙發裡，持刀的兇手發出邪惡的笑聲，刀尖閃著刺眼的白光，下一秒——"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_orangefall"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經典！震撼！不愧是我最喜歡的恐怖電影，哪怕是三十多年前的小成本製作，跟現在的新片比起來也毫不遜色！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……還是看恐怖片比較能發洩情緒，我好像沒有那麼焦慮了。謝謝你的邀請，小蒂比。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#2$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大聲喊出來舒服多了吧，謝莉小姐？我就說你不是故意打斷拍攝的，只是最近神經太緊繃了。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，雖然還有一些問題沒解決……但今晚就讓我忘記它們吧。接下來我們看什麼？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#2$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應有盡有，恐怖電影之夜才剛剛開始呢！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？莫麗，你怎麼一直不說話，是不喜歡這部電影嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電影裡出現的武器刀刃太過輕薄，如果是我就乾脆設計更特殊的武器，在側面加上血溝造型，視覺上的衝擊力也更強！", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再想工作了！莫麗！你是不是跟謝莉小姐待太久了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_MCcat_1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喵~", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？你怎麼在這裡啊，神秘的小傢伙。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "美麗的生物緩步走到兩個小女孩中間，展示般地伸了一個懶腰，端坐在沙發前。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗你看，她好像真的很喜歡我們呢。那就跟我們一起看電影吧！千萬別被嚇到了哦。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？誰的終端響了？莫麗，是你的嗎？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是啊。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#3$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我得……先走了。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的臉色好差，不會是因為白天的事被格蕾塔女士責備了吧？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗，明天我們再幫她分擔一些工作吧？謝莉小姐看起來真的很疲憊。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來！我們接著看電影，下一部恐怖片拿過最佳設計獎哦，布景、道具和武器都做得非常酷……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "螢光閃爍，兩個女孩再次沉浸在新的驚悚故事裡，絲毫沒注意到腳邊的Miss.Christine也已悄無聲息地離開。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g1_setting_lobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5, "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉？你不是應該在跟小蒂比她們看電影嗎？這麼急著是想去哪裡？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "語氣親暱的男子注意到謝莉的右手緊緊抓著終端。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，我知道了……突然收到了約會邀請？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下千萬別向對方露出這樣沉重的表情啊，他會傷心的。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟你無關。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的嘴唇在顫抖。你很冷，還是說在害怕？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可憐的小傢伙，你也跟我一樣，被道爾頓的意外嚇壞了，對嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別憂心了，有你這麼認真的統籌，我相信接下來一切都會很順利的。來，讓我給你個擁抱，你會暖和一點……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“跟你一樣”？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從你的甜言蜜語裡聽不到半點恐懼。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的記憶力已經差到連五年前發生的事都能從腦海裡抹得一乾二淨了嗎？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法“跟你一樣”沒心沒肺……別忘了，你也要為當初的墜亡事故負責。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "300,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g13_directorstudio", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深夜，二樓的辦公室燈突然亮了起來。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一張辦公桌上，資料夾中的文件被整齊地收納著，幾乎看不出有人使用的痕跡。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而另一張桌子上，通告單雜亂無章，布滿修改痕跡，似乎字跡的主人正被什麼困擾。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個高挑的身影在辦公桌附近翻找著什麼，動作精準俐落，沒發出一絲聲響。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機有近期使用過的痕跡。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩打開集紙匣，在大量碎紙條中撿出了觸感特別的幾條——那些不是劇組的列印紙。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“特里蒙大學”……“環境監測”……簽名是……格蕾塔。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是謝莉所說的“奇怪的文件”。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他感覺自己的肩膀被輕輕推了一下，像一聲認同，但辦公室內除了自己以外再無旁人。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎回來，Miss.Christine。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#11$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近你散步的次數變多了，是找到什麼感興趣的東西嗎？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#12$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡比想像中更有趣。", "name": "Miss.Christine"}, "figure_art": "avg_4198_christ_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我也發現了意料之外的東西。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#5$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……別想太多……你只是來確認到底是誰的惡作劇……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你親眼看著那個號碼作廢，不可能是那個人……不可能……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉努力平復著自己的心情，觀影時刻意遺忘的恐懼和焦慮此刻再度淹沒了她。"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“去倉庫，去贖你的罪。”"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終端螢幕在寂靜的倉庫裡微微發光，寄件人一欄裡跳動著謝莉熟悉卻難以面對的名字——“勞拉”。"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glass_break"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰在那裡！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要再裝神弄鬼了，我現在很清楚這則訊息不是我的幻覺！你到底要幹嘛……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道什麼？！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無人回應。黑暗吞沒了老舊倉庫裡所有殘存的聲音。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "細小的電流聲簌簌作響，遠處貨架上的頂燈突然亮起。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詭異而充滿誘惑，謝莉控制不住地向光源走去。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉小姐。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……勞拉……是你嗎……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉再次顫抖起來，她無法分辨這個聲音究竟來自倉庫深處，還是自己的幻想。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她呆呆地向前走著，彷彿回到了五年前的攝影棚，悲劇一幕的開場。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉，謝莉！我又新加了一場戲，需要用到吊鋼絲，你可以幫我準備一下嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狂妄……自傲……目中無人……你是個在藍卡塢剛剛起步的新人，怎麼敢……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓先生說他已經徵得導演的同意，這個應該是已經確定了……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正值事業巔峰的道爾頓想教訓你，你卻還誤以為他是真的想幫你……結果呢，你滿意了嗎？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他還沒來嗎……我都在鋼絲上吊了好幾個小時了，腿和手臂大概都磨破皮了……謝莉，可以請你幫我問一下他們嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是“一個統籌”而已，只配幫你準備鋼絲和設備，保證它們是……安全的……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你做到了嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉走到貨架前，燈光明晃晃地照著一個黑色的防塵袋，她知道裡面是什麼。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要打開，謝莉，不要。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_zipper_normal", "loop": "true", "channel": "v"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "v", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！！！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "防塵袋裡裝著一套老舊的吊掛設備，挂鉤和吊索磨損得很嚴重，安全帶也幾近斷裂。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑色的布料上沾染著一些深色的斑塊。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是勞拉的血。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不！你不可能知道！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我的幻覺！你不可能還活著！對了……疼痛……鋼筆，我帶了鋼筆……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerslow", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.7, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……可悲。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你還在……為什麼沒有用！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "五年前的事故，究竟是意外還是謀殺？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是意外……是意外！要不是道爾頓故意為難你，根本沒有後面的慘劇！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不檢查我身上的設備？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.8, "ato": 0.8}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1848_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我恨你！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我恨你自私、傲慢，把劇組的日程搞得一團糟，所有人的工作都被你無理取鬧的要求影響！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#5$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓想要教訓你，那當然好！我那天像往常一樣檢查吊掛設備，卻發現它剛好到了更換日期……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我腦中閃過一個很小很小的念頭——要是你出了意外徹底消失……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈……哈哈……那不就更好了嗎……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_doorclose"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blizzard", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_icecage", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻手將神情恍惚的謝莉推倒在地，她聽到冷媒在管道中汩汩流動，厚實的冰霜在她身下緩緩開裂。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉這才意識到，自己不知不覺走進了倉庫盡頭的冷凍庫。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "砸門？吼叫？謝莉已無力掙扎。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐懼不知不覺消失了，她感到前所未有的放鬆。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡將所有謎題的答案都給她了。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}